# Workspace runtime storage: SQLite database plus SQLite write-ahead log
# files produced by cedar-intent at runtime. The directory is created by
# ``cedar-intent init`` and must never be committed because it contains
# deployment history and per-deployment secrets (for example, deployment
# response bodies captured during HTTP pushes).
.cedar-intent/
.cedar-intent/*

